    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン、ここはいったん退こう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon, let's withdraw for right now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>くっ、やむを得ないか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kh. I suppose there's nothing else we can do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、マルタ。
あの人たちの言ってた事って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, Marta. The stuff those guys were saying...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あんなの嘘に決まってるよ。
だってパパの話とぜんぜんちがうもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Obviously those guys were lying.
I mean, that's totally not what Papa told me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そう……なのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is... that right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだよ。
パパが嘘つくはずないもの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. Papa wouldn't lie to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからね、行こ。
私のエミル〜♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So let's go. My Emil〜♪.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちょ、ちょっと！
なんでくっつくの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Wait! Why are you clinging to me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え〜ダメなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whaaat? Should I not?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ダメじゃないけど……ダメだってば！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's not that you can't... Just don't!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ふふ、どっちかわかんないから
くっついとくね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ehehe. I don't know which one it is,
so I'm gonna hold onto you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
